        <h3>Getting Started</h3>
        <p class="lead">After installing the Alpheios Reading Tools extension for <a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/alpheios-reading-tools/apkmkeppocbbebomnhdmhfenfifkhjfd">Chrome</a> or Firefox, the Alpheios icon will be
